snippet.textDisplay:
Hi guys, it is not a general-purpose hospital.
But guess what? There will be CT room, X-ray room, the operating room, receiving clinic, laboratory a centralized patient management computer and network equipment room, a morgue with necessary refrigeration, a reception area, a negative pressure ward building, some ICU rooms, a medical technology building, a central supply warehouse, a garbage treatment temporary storage room, a ambulance washing room, medical staff access and patient access, special sanitary passage facilities for air shower, Oxygen stations, morgues, incinerators, septic tanks and other facilities, as well as special access channels, special access for medical staff, disinfection system, call system, suction system, oxygen pipeline system, sewage treatment system, living supply center, liquefied gas supply station, rain cover, and other isolation facilities.

And Each ward is designed according to two rooms, about 18 square meters, are equipped with oxygen supply system, negative pressure suction system, etc. The ward is equipped with its own bathroom, which is equipped with toilets, grab bars and showers.Double glazing for food delivery; Installation of air primary filtration treatment facilities, oxygen and vacuum suction centralized supply facilities; Ultraviolet disinfection lamp, television, air conditioning

The construction land of 50,000 square meters is fully covered by anti-seepage film, and the sewage will be disinfected for 4 hours before entering the urban pipe network. The rainwater in the site will be collected comprehensively through a special system, disinfected for half an hour before entering the urban pipe network, and the medical waste will be specially disposed according to the relevant regulations of the environmental protection department.

In terms of network and communication, the hospital adopts fully covered 5G network communication design, VR/AR telemedicine system, APP online interactive platform and other technologies. The communication adopts double operator, double route and double core to ensure the security and reliability of the communication system.

Every worker could get 200-250 US Dollors per day , and they are all heros, should be paid more.

Chinese are trying our best to stop the spread of the virus, this virus will kill everyone in the world, it is time we should be united.
